caption: Had the Chicken Philly with vegan cheese and loved it! Appreciate that I can choose vegan cheese with my meat entree since I'm not vegan I just have a stomach that does not agree with dairy. Great service too!👏🏼

They just reopened and everything is made to impress. Loving the addition of the beyond meat for the vegan cheesesteak option. The crispy buffalo chicken salad is so tasty! But what really stole my heart is the Quesadilla take on the Philly Cheesesteak. It's basically a Phillydilla! Way to californicate it guys haha!
